awrah","tag-prayer-al-salat"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9Mi","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":28177,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-eight-rakaat-forenoon\/","url_meta":{"origin":37590,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Duha: The Prophet prays eight cycles in forenoon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Hani\u2019 reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace blessings be upon him, in the year of the liberation, and I found him taking a bath. When the Prophet finished his bath, he performed eight cycles of prayer, and that was in the forenoon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 357,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14165,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/13\/something-happens-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":37590,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: If something happens during the prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGlorification of Allah is for men and clapping is for women.\u201d Ibn al-Muthna added, \"If something happens in prayer.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1145, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 423 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/11\/hypocrites-if-they-knew-crawl\/","url_meta":{"origin":37590,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: They would crawl to prayer if they knew","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"No prayer is more burdensome to the hypocrites than the dawn and evening prayers. If they knew the blessing in them, they would come even if they had to crawl.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 657, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 651 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25820,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/28\/salat-private-conversation\/","url_meta":{"origin":37590,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Believer in private conversation with Allah in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer in prayer is in a private conversation with his Lord. Let him not spit in front of him, nor to his right side, but rather to his left side or beneath his feet.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/13\/salat-shortened-two-rakaat-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":37590,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Prayer shortened to two cycles during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I accompanied the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and during travel he would not add more to his prayer than two cycles. Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman did likewise, may Allah be pleased with them. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1051, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 689 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/sajdah-salat-not-like-kalb\/","url_meta":{"origin":37590,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Keep forearms raised in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe straight in prostration and let none of you put his forearms on the ground like a dog.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 788, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 493 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_li